.SH "Detailed Description"
.PP 
Attach this script directly to: Detective Sheet Panel SETUP: 


.IP "1." 4
Select "Detective Sheet Panel" in the Hierarchy\&.
.IP "2." 4
Inspector → Add Component → \fBDetectiveSheetManager\fP\&.
.IP "3." 4
Leave the sheetPanel field empty — it auto-assigns to this GameObject\&.
.IP "4." 4
Drag "Detective Button" (inside Options Panel) into the detectiveButton slot\&.
.IP "5." 4
The panel will be hidden automatically on Play — no need to set it inactive\&. 
